[
  {
    "startTime": 4.4,
    "endTime": 8.48,
    "text": "In this lesson, we are going  to focus on past simple."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.24,
    "endTime": 14.08,
    "text": "Past simple is used to talk  about finished actions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.76,
    "endTime": 21.12,
    "text": "For regular verb forms we use 'ed' to describe the past tense."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.64,
    "endTime": 29.84,
    "text": "For example: 'I walk to school'  becomes 'Yesterday, I \"walked\" to school.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.2,
    "endTime": 37.135,
    "text": "Most of the very common verbs are irregular, so it's important that we know these."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.135,
    "endTime": 53.8,
    "text": "Have/had, do/did , say/said,  go/went , give/gave, get/got, make/made."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.8,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "Know/knew,  is/was , am/was , are/were."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.64,
    "endTime": 68.4,
    "text": "For example: 'I usually \"eat\" lunch in the kitchen.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.68,
    "endTime": 73.058,
    "text": "'Yesterday I \"ate\" lunch at the park.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.68,
    "endTime": 79.84,
    "text": "In Episode 2 of 'Fortune Blue', Daniel  and Jimmy talk about the past."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.72,
    "endTime": 85.84,
    "text": "They use the verbs 'give', 'get' and 'take'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.48,
    "endTime": 89.909,
    "text": "Do you know the past form for these three verbs?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.24,
    "endTime": 94.74,
    "text": "-I got desperate and low on information."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.74,
    "endTime": 96.771,
    "text": "-You gave them empty files."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.111,
    "endTime": 99.839,
    "text": "-And took their money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.48,
    "endTime": 103.917,
    "text": "Let's check the answers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.851,
    "endTime": 108.984,
    "text": "-I 'got' desperate and low on information."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.984,
    "endTime": 111.06299999999999,
    "text": "-You 'gave' them empty files."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.219,
    "endTime": 113.881,
    "text": "-And 'took' their money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.634,
    "endTime": 118.633,
    "text": "So, were you correct?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 125.658,
    "text": "As a final activity, let's look at some of the most common verb forms."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.56,
    "endTime": 128.099,
    "text": "Do you know all of them?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.099,
    "endTime": 132.20499999999998,
    "text": "think/thought."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.205,
    "endTime": 136.375,
    "text": "come/came."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.375,
    "endTime": 140.611,
    "text": "tell/told."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.611,
    "endTime": 144.86399999999998,
    "text": "leave/left."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.864,
    "endTime": 149.0,
    "text": "put/put."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.0,
    "endTime": 153.221,
    "text": "talk/talked."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.221,
    "endTime": 157.50300000000001,
    "text": "find/found."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.503,
    "endTime": 161.67999999999998,
    "text": "hear/heard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.68,
    "endTime": 165.934,
    "text": "show/showed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.934,
    "endTime": 169.44,
    "text": "write/wrote."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.44,
    "endTime": 174.273,
    "text": "Remember, past simple is used  to talk about finished actions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.273,
    "endTime": 176.84799999999998,
    "text": "I hope you enjoyed this grammar lesson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.848,
    "endTime": 183.04000000000002,
    "text": "See you next time."
  }
]